author: Rob Braxman Tech
description:
Shipping of BraX3 has been delayed to June 2025. We will talk about a significant issue that we were unaware of with iODE OS and the solution planned. This problem prevented the final production of phones at the factory. I will explain the specific problem which has to do with IMEI and how it will be handled. So bear with us a moment more and we will get through this!
